      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. i'll add the initialization for state_variable now. but the whole thing feels really random. like, why does the timeout only happen during these specific spikes, and then the code just breaks in a different way? it feels like there's something weird or \"unpredictable\" going on with the environment itself. any idea why it feels so unstable?",
